applied. The Gower distance between objects \emph{i} and \emph{j} is
computed by
\eqn{d_{ij} = 1 - s_{ij}}, where
\deqn{s_{ij} = \frac{\sum_{l=1}^p \omega_{ijl} s_{ijl}}
{\sum_{l=1}^p \omega_{ijl}}}
